    <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        How to Choose the Right Cannabis Dispensary
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        With hundreds of dispensaries in most legal states, choosing the right one can be overwhelming. This step-by-step guide
        helps you evaluate options, compare key factors, and find a dispensary that matches your specific needs and preferences.
      </p>

      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 1: Define Your Priorities</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Before researching dispensaries, identify what matters most to you. Different customers prioritize different factors.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Key Decision Factors</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Product-Focused</h4>
              <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Wide selection of strains</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Organic/premium options</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Specific product types (edibles, concentrates)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Lab testing transparency</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Convenience-Focused</h4>
              <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Close to home/work</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Extended hours</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Delivery service</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Online ordering</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Price-Focused</h4>
              <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Competitive everyday pricing</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Regular deals and discounts</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Loyalty rewards program</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Bulk pricing options</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Service-Focused</h4>
              <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Knowledgeable budtenders</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Personalized recommendations</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Educational resources</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Welcoming atmosphere</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 2: Research Local Options</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Use Online Directories</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Start with dispensary directories to get a comprehensive view of your options:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Our Rankings:</strong> Browse state and county-specific rankings based on reviews, ratings, and community feedback</li>
          <li><strong>Google Maps:</strong> Search "dispensary near me" to see proximity and basic info</li>
          <li><strong>Specialized Platforms:</strong> Leafly, Weedmaps for detailed menus and reviews</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Read Reviews Critically</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Reviews provide valuable insights, but read them strategically:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-yellow-50 border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-green-900 mb-2">‚úì Look For:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-green-800 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ 4+ star average rating</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ High review volume (100+ reviews)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Recent reviews (last 3-6 months)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Consistent positive themes</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Detailed, thoughtful feedback</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Management responses to complaints</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-red-900 mb-2">‚úó Red Flags:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-red-800 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Below 3.5 star average</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Very few total reviews</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ All reviews from same timeframe (fake)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Recurring complaints (quality, service)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ No management responses</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Reports of aggressive upselling</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 3: Compare Product Selection and Quality</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Check Online Menus</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Most dispensaries post their menus online. Evaluate:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Variety:</strong> Do they carry 20+ strains or just a handful?</li>
          <li><strong>Product Types:</strong> Full selection of flower, edibles, concentrates, vapes, topicals?</li>
          <li><strong>Brands:</strong> Recognized, reputable brands or unknown names?</li>
          <li><strong>Potency Range:</strong> Options for both light users and heavy consumers?</li>
          <li><strong>Stock Levels:</strong> Frequently sold out or well-stocked?</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Verify Quality Standards</h3>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3"><strong>Quality Indicators:</strong></p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>‚úì Lab testing results readily available (COAs)</li>
            <li>‚úì Organic or pesticide-free options</li>
            <li>‚úì Proper storage conditions (humidity-controlled)</li>
            <li>‚úì Fresh products (recent harvest dates)</li>
            <li>‚úì Multiple price tiers (budget to premium)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 4: Evaluate Pricing and Value</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Compare Base Prices</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Cannabis pricing varies significantly. Compare apples-to-apples:
        </p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white border">
            <thead class="bg-gray-100">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 border text-left">Product Type</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 border text-left">Typical Price Range</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 border text-left">What to Compare</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-sm">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Flower (1/8 oz)</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">$25-$60</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Price per gram, THC %</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Edibles (10-pack)</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">$15-$40</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Price per mg of THC</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Vape Cartridge (1g)</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">$30-$70</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Brand quality, potency</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Concentrates (1g)</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">$20-$80</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 border">Extract type, purity</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Look for Deals and Discounts</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Daily Deals:</strong> Many dispensaries have daily specials (e.g., "Wax Wednesday," "Flower Friday")</li>
          <li><strong>Happy Hours:</strong> Discounted pricing during slow hours</li>
          <li><strong>First-Time Customer:</strong> Often 10-25% off your first purchase</li>
          <li><strong>Loyalty Programs:</strong> Points-based rewards (typically earn $1 per $10-20 spent)</li>
          <li><strong>Medical Discounts:</strong> Veterans, seniors, low-income, industry workers</li>
          <li><strong>Bulk Discounts:</strong> Better per-unit pricing on larger quantities</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-900">
            <strong>Warning:</strong> Extremely low prices can indicate lower quality. If a deal seems too good to be true, check reviews carefully.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 5: Assess Location and Convenience</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Evaluate Accessibility</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">üó∫Ô∏è Location Factors</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-blue-800 space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Distance from home/work</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Ease of parking</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Public transportation access</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Safe neighborhood</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Other errands nearby</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">‚è∞ Hours & Services</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-blue-800 space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Operating hours (match your schedule?)</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Weekend/holiday hours</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Online ordering/pickup</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Delivery service</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Curbside pickup</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 6: Consider Atmosphere and Service</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">What Reviews Say About Service</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Pay attention to how reviews describe the customer experience:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Staff Knowledge:</strong> Do budtenders provide helpful recommendations?</li>
          <li><strong>Wait Times:</strong> Are customers in and out quickly or waiting 30+ minutes?</li>
          <li><strong>Atmosphere:</strong> Welcoming and professional or rushed and impersonal?</li>
          <li><strong>New Customer Experience:</strong> Patient with beginners or dismissive?</li>
          <li><strong>Problem Resolution:</strong> How do they handle complaints or product issues?</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Step 7: Visit in Person</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Try Before You Commit</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Narrow your list to 2-3 dispensaries and visit each:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">What to Observe:</h4>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
            <li>‚úì Cleanliness and organization</li>
            <li>‚úì Staff friendliness and knowledge</li>
            <li>‚úì Wait time and efficiency</li>
            <li>‚úì Product presentation</li>
            <li>‚úì Overall vibe and comfort</li>
            <li>‚úì Security and safety measures</li>
            <li>‚úì Payment options</li>
            <li>‚úì First impression</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Ask These Questions</h3>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>"What are your most popular strains/products?"</li>
          <li>"Do you have first-time customer discounts?"</li>
          <li>"Can I see lab results for this product?"</li>
          <li>"Do you offer delivery or online ordering?"</li>
          <li>"What's your return/exchange policy?"</li>
          <li>"Do you have a loyalty program?"</li>
        </ol>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Special Considerations</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">For Medical Patients</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you're a medical marijuana patient, prioritize:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Medical-Specific Products:</strong> High-CBD options, specific cannabinoid ratios</li>
          <li><strong>Compassion Programs:</strong> Financial assistance for low-income patients</li>
          <li><strong>Consultation Services:</strong> Staff trained in medical cannabis applications</li>
          <li><strong>Higher Purchase Limits:</strong> Medical patients often can buy more than recreational</li>
          <li><strong>Tax Benefits:</strong> Some states exempt medical patients from certain taxes</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">For Budget-Conscious Shoppers</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>Look for dispensaries with robust daily deal calendars</li>
          <li>Join multiple loyalty programs to maximize rewards</li>
          <li>Buy in bulk when quality products go on sale</li>
          <li>Consider "shake" or "popcorn" buds for significant savings</li>
          <li>Ask about house brands (often 20-30% cheaper than name brands)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">For Premium Seekers</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>Seek out dispensaries specializing in craft cannabis</li>
          <li>Look for exclusive or limited-release strains</li>
          <li>Prioritize dispensaries with in-house growing operations</li>
          <li>Check for organic certification or pesticide-free guarantees</li>
          <li>Ask about small-batch, hand-trimmed products</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Making Your Decision</h2>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Decision Framework</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Score each dispensary on these criteria (1-5 scale):
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Product Quality & Selection:</strong> ___ / 5</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Pricing & Value:</strong> ___ / 5</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Location & Convenience:</strong> ___ / 5</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Staff Knowledge & Service:</strong> ___ / 5</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Atmosphere & Cleanliness:</strong> ___ / 5</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Reviews & Reputation:</strong> ___ / 5</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4 font-semibold">
            Total Score: ___ / 30
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Final Tips</h2>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-8">
          <li><strong>You're Not Locked In:</strong> Feel free to shop around. Many people use different dispensaries for different needs.</li>
          <li><strong>Build Relationships:</strong> Once you find a favorite budtender, they'll remember your preferences and make better recommendations.</li>
          <li><strong>Stay Flexible:</strong> Product availability changes. Your go-to dispensary might not always have what you want.</li>
          <li><strong>Prioritize Safety:</strong> Never compromise on licensing, lab testing, or professionalism for lower prices.</li>
          <li><strong>Trust Your Gut:</strong> If something feels off about a dispensary, trust that instinct.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Find Your Perfect Dispensary</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">Browse verified reviews and ratings to discover top dispensaries in your area</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-white text-green-600 font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
            Explore Dispensary Rankings
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
